                                <a href="/causes">What's this?</a></td>
							</tr>
                         </table>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
					</div><ul class="links"><li class="0 first"><span title="Comments" rel="nofollow"><a href='#comments' ><img src = '/sites/all/themes/mnn/img/service-icons/v-comment.png' alt='' /> Comments (30)</a></span></li>
